"https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/beltoft-gift-cards-for-woocommerce/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: beltoft-gift-cards.php
msgid ""
"Sell digital gift cards, deliver them by email, and let customers redeem "
"them at checkout."
msgstr ""
"Venda cartões-presente digitais, envie-os por e-mail e permita que os "
"clientes os resgatem no checkout."

